    "updated_at": "2012-11-20T13:08:46Z",
    "body": "Looks like there are indeed memory leaks. I didn't know about the OSX tool [Instruments](https://developer.apple.com/library/mac/#documentation/DeveloperTools/Conceptual/InstrumentsUserGuide/Introduction/Introduction.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40004652-CH1-SW1), but I was able to spot the cause of one of the leaks with it immediately. It is still reporting leaks though so I'll have to take a closer look at what the cause of the others might be."
